item.description:
This is going to be a fast paced and beautiful walk that will go through the Wellesley College Arboretum and around Lake Waban. We will meet at 5:30 at the Wellesley Square Commuter Rail Station and start walking at 5:40. The walk will last 1 Â½ - 2 hours. We should easily complete the Arboretum and Lake Waban before the 7:28 sunset. The portion from Lake Waban back to Wellesley Square is light with lamps.

Let's meet at 5:30 at the Wellesley Square Commuter Rail Station. There is parking and also commuter rail trains that will take you to Wellesley Square. I can give people a ride to the Riverside on the way back.
item.name: Lake Waban in Wellesley - Fast Paced Workout and Beautiful Late Day Walk
